1) Install the tools to build
On debian squeeze : build-essential python-crypto python-pip
2) 0MQ
- Install the software from the source or through your package manager if it is available
Download page : http://www.zeromq.org/intro:get-the-software
Direct download : http://download.zeromq.org/zeromq-2.1.10.tar.gz
Untar/make install
3) Paramiko
- Install the lib
Website : http://www.lag.net/paramiko/
4) Launch
